{"tid":377523,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"數學堂又說星數目難知道","createTime":"2017-08-27T17:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T06:02:36.000Z","uid":1706,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0261e5c599b3616167fbada45a48b0c03290ec","tid":377523,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:56:49.000Z","msg":"我每夜望但見空蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哪兒望見星每夜來閃照 數著入睡到天亮<br />\n哪兒若有天雨後虹彩降 可給我張望<br />\n哪兒讓我找老樹來依傍<br />\n那麼空矌那麼廣闊那麼清朗<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日個腦係咁loop呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有阿花的故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd2acd765e9babd2bba9633f7ce41a2027fe0e3","tid":377523,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜無人聽過？"},{"pid":"a25641ebbc34a70bbfe066b198797be91b971485","tid":377523,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790b517677755b667ebbd3f6bcdf06140905fa61","tid":377523,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001eaa4cca1e043ac4257550df6057d02a0aaf80","tid":377523,"uid":26072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:52:00.000Z","msg":"無人理....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c765971910dfa8cc475f19d134be96417b9cce0c","tid":377523,"uid":26072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:52:28.000Z","msg":"正評我既"},{"pid":"cbd5911f55e52a233b275107e8dded7d8531dd8c",